{
 "name": "RPlog_Joir_in_Command",
 "title": "Joir Takes Command",
 "summary": "Director Joir, of the Bureau of Operations, is received in the office of Grand Admiral Adlerson to discuss disturbing rumors about the Bureau's stability. Coldly composed, Joir presents a datapad and explains that Lord Atrox is his main concern but that his own role has come into question. Adlerson confirms that the Emperor has removed Atrox from command of the Bureau, leaving Joir to lead the branch until a new Director is appointed. Joir accepts the added responsibility with characteristic emotionless control, pledging to serve the Emperor, and departs after a curt exchange of military courtesies.",
